---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`Experience | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="My professional experience" />
		<style>
			main {
				max-width: 1200px;
			}
			
			.page-header {
				padding: 4rem 0 3rem 0;
			}
			
			.page-title {
				font-size: 3.5rem;
				font-weight: 800;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				color: var(--text-primary);
			}
			
			.page-subtitle {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				color: var(--text-tertiary);
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}
			
			.intro-text {
				font-size: 1.125rem;
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				line-height: 1.8;
				max-width: 900px;
				margin-bottom: 4rem;
			}
			
			.timeline {
				position: relative;
				margin-bottom: 4rem;
			}
			
			.timeline-item {
				position: relative;
				padding-left: 3rem;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
			}
			
			.timeline-item::before {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				left: 0;
				top: 0.5rem;
				width: 1rem;
				height: 1rem;
				border-radius: 50%;
				background: var(--accent);
			}
			
			.timeline-item::after {
				content: '';
				position: absolute;
				left: 0.4375rem;
				top: 1.5rem;
				bottom: -3rem;
				width: 2px;
				background: var(--border-color);
			}
			
			.timeline-item:last-child::after {
				display: none;
			}
			
			.experience-header {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 1rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
			}
			
			.experience-title {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				color: var(--text-primary);
				margin: 0;
			}
			
			.experience-badge {
				padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
				background: var(--accent);
				color: white;
				border-radius: 6px;
				font-size: 0.875rem;
				font-weight: 600;
			}
			
			.experience-date {
				color: var(--text-tertiary);
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}
			
			.experience-description {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				line-height: 1.7;
			}
			
			.nav-links {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				padding: 2rem 0;
				border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
			}
			
			.nav-link {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 0.5rem;
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				text-decoration: none;
				transition: color 0.2s ease;
			}
			
			.nav-link:hover {
				color: var(--accent);
			}
			
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.page-title {
					font-size: 2.5rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="page-header">
				<h1 class="page-title">Experience</h1>
				<p class="page-subtitle">You need it to get the job, but the job's what gives it!</p>
			</section>

			<p class="intro-text">
				Throughout my journey as a developer, I have had the opportunity to work with cutting-edge technologies
				while also mastering the fine art of debugging at 2 AM. From building dynamic web applications to
				deciphering cryptic error messages, my experience has been a mix of structured learning and
				spontaneous problem-solving. Each project and internship has sharpened my ability to write clean code,
				collaborate effectively, and most importantly—fix bugs before they fix me.
			</p>

			<div class="timeline">
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="experience-header">
						<h3 class="experience-title">Senior Technical Lead • OneOrigin</h3>
						<span class="experience-badge">Latest</span>
					</div>
					<p class="experience-date">2023 - Present</p>
					<p class="experience-description">
						Architected and scaled enterprise cloud/web platforms, boosting release velocity by 40%. 
						Built AI automation frameworks cutting manual operations by 60%. Designed multi-tenant 
						systems for thousands of users and mentored 10+ engineers, helping them grow into strategic 
						technical leaders.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="experience-header">
						<h3 class="experience-title">Senior Software Engineer • OneOrigin</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="experience-date">2022 - 2023</p>
					<p class="experience-description">
						Migrated monolith to microservices architecture, achieving 50% faster deployments. Integrated 
						AI modules for automation and insights, increasing UX engagement by 25%. Delivered projects 
						under budget with CI/CD improvements and infrastructure optimization.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="experience-header">
						<h3 class="experience-title">Technical Team Lead • OneOrigin</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="experience-date">2020 - 2022</p>
					<p class="experience-description">
						Led distributed teams building high-availability systems. Owned SDLC for platforms with 
						50K+ active users. Reduced production incidents by 35% with automation and monitoring 
						improvements. Established engineering best practices and mentored junior developers.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="experience-header">
						<h3 class="experience-title">Intern • cityon.net</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="experience-date">2016</p>
					<p class="experience-description">
						Early UI development work, building foundations in CSS, JavaScript (ES6), and modern 
						web development practices. Contributed to responsive web interfaces and learned 
						collaborative software development workflows.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="nav-links">
				<a href="/skills" class="nav-link">
					<span>←</span>
					<span>Skills & Tools</span>
				</a>
				<a href="/education" class="nav-link">
					<span>Education</span>
					<span>→</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
